<p>Administrative notes:</p>
<p>None of the content in this GitHub repository is considered proprietary or procurement-sensitive information.
Furthermore, all users who submit bids consent to the publication of their GitHub usernames and bid amounts following the conclusion of the bidding process.
Bidders' email addresses will not be disclosed and will only be used for micro-purchase-related communication on an as-needed basis.</p>

<P>This platform is the primary method of bidding on micro-purchase opportunities. Vendor organizations may have multiple user accounts registered on this micro-purchase platform and on GitHub, as well as associated with each vendor and the vendor's DUNS number. Furthermore, vendors may register as either individuals or businesses on SAM.gov. Please file a GitHub issue <a href="https://github.com/18F/micropurchase/issues">in this repo</a> if you have any questions.</p>
